<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kayzen Izumi API</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="hero">
        <div class="banner-bg"></div>
        <div class="profile-container">
            <img src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Kayzen Izumi" class="profile-pic">
            <h1>Kayzen Izumi</h1>
            <p class="tagline">Developer & Bot Enthusiast</p>
            <div class="buttons">
                <a href="/docs" class="btn">Buka Dokumentasi</a>
                <a href="#about" class="btn btn-outline">About Me</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="slider-container">
        <h2>Cosplay Gallery</h2>
        <div class="slider-wrapper">
            <div class="slider-track">
                <% for(let i=1; i<=15; i++) { %>
                    <div class="slide"><img src="/images/slide<%= i %>.jpg" alt="Slide <%= i %>"></div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="info-section" id="about">
        <div class="card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-user"></i> About Kayzen Izumi</h3>
            <p>Halo, saya Kayzen Izumi. Seorang pengembang yang berfokus pada JavaScript dan Bot Automation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-code"></i> About Web Ini</h3>
            <p>Web API ini dibangun sebagai layanan RESTful gratis yang menyediakan berbagai fitur scraping.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer><p>&copy; 2025 Kayzen Izumi.</p></footer>
</body>
</html>
